title: DeHaven Irby Talks The Streets & Jay-Z Betrayel

Tonight we kicked it with former Marcy projects baller DeHaven Irby. We talk about the 80's and 90's NYC dope game, how the internet has damn near drove everybody crazy and of course why he felt Jay-Z, Dame and Biggs did him dirty.... Tap IN
